Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made a raid on the Navy HQ to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who was to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his struggle ended in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the historic War of the \NBest in Marineford has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, 10 years ago, in the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, this is Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna live here with them from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you! Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Here Comes Sabo! The Boy \Nat the Gray Terminal!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we earned this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porchemy-san was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That greedy merchant begged for it when we \Nsaid that it was treasure from the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it was just junk that \Nwe found washed up on the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were lucky that he was just a \Ncoward who has never gone to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:05:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've never been to sea, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a place like this on the North side \Nof Mt. Corvo where the Dadan family lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a smoky pile of discarded junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unwanted things ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here live rogues who were \Nshunned from mainstream society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsurprisingly, it's a lawless area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crime and disease abound \Nsince there are no doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is called Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's afternoon already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure, treasure! Is there \Nanything valuable here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give it to me!\N--That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me cash it in for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can't have it!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn you!\N--Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have gotten hurt \Nif you'd just given it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Or I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:25.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"THE FOREST IN-BETWEEN" \NMT COLVO AND GRAY TERMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo! Sabo, are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:36.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already done some work in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:42.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SABO [10 YEARS OLD] (A BOY WHO \NLIVES IN THE GRAY TERMINAL)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Well, I did, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You got a lot! Way more than I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of money! How'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I robbed some thugs near the main gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! You won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 5 years since we started \Nto put money in our "pirate savings".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We worked hard for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna leave the East Blue and go \Nsomewhere these people have never dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exciting just to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now put it away. We can't \Nlet anybody to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much we need \Nto get a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. 10 million \Nor 100 million maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A pirate ship"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Are you gonna become pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Be quiet!\N--Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! I didn't know that you \Ntravel this far everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Luffy that \Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you told him about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him how annoying you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also told me that you're empty-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't realize that \Nwe're dissing you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally got me here although I \Ndidn't take any walkable routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Ace's? \NBe my friend, too, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You can't call me "buddy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then what's your name?\N--Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you to live here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The daily round trip--training on the \Nmountain road turned out to be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He found our secret. He's gonna \Ntell somebody if nothing is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill me!! Help me!! I don't wanna die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, kill him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never killed anybody before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither! And I don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw me into water!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, let's head to the river!\N--Why did he tell us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up!\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear a voice from the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Somebody's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set him free for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta move from \Nhere or they're gonna find our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows those kids \Naround here. Ace and Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:13.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that it was \NAce who took the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:18.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CREW MEMBER OF THE BLUEJAM PIRATES PORCHEMY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We're sorry. We shouldn't \Nlet our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How outrageous that kid is! \NHe can't just steal our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Captain Bluejam finds out about \Nthis, he's gonna kill all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I didn't know that those \Nthugs were working for Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that you stole the money from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have taken that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a real sword. That's \NPorchemy who works under Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:13:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He strips off your scalp alive \Nafter you lose a fight with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just let them pass for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let me go! What do you want from me?\N--How could you get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this little shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That fool! He's calling my name!\N--Help me! Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call for "Ace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but he just tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool! He's such a big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you know about this but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Ace stole some \Nmoney from us and ran today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know where is it now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! They're gonna take \Nall our treasure away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that fool doesn't tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright! It can't be \Nhelped that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll help you \Nbring back the memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Let me \Ngo! Where are you taking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Stupid! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Let me go! What \Nare you doing, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what we have to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that my body turned to \Nrubber after I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Fruit, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you had the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a pair of gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, hurry up! We're \Nscrewed if they come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta move our treasure somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of time \Nbefore Luffy tells them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take not only what we stole from them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but all of our "pirate savings" that \Nwe've spent 5 years collecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money that your friend Ace stole \Nis very important to our pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I need you to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna make a pirate mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain Bluejam is very brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, go look for Ace and Sabo! We \Ndon't have time to stand around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me if I know Ace and Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must be hooligans from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna mess with those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're kids but you \Ncan't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like mad dogs \Nthat'd kill even a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Sabo? I haven't \Nseen them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, young men, why don't you \Nleave everything valuable here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--C-Come on, man!\N--We'll ask someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still don't know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that they'd know by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize that it's almost night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We moved all the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:19:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo! What's wrong? Have they \Nshown up to look for the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I bet they won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't told them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that they're torturing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that he'd just tell them \Nbecause he's dumb and cries so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GRAY TERMINAL "THE COVE OF PIRATES"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is in charge today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Porchemy, Captain Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that they've already \Ncashed it in by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's running away with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:20:01.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CAPTAIN OF THE BLUEJAM PIRATES BLUEJAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I don't think that he would risk \Ngetting killed trying something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-Porchemy-san! \NIt's no use doing it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the energy \Nto even scream now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he won't say anything and to be \Nhonest, I can't stand watching it--it's too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show some mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for Ace and Sabo if you \Nhave time to speak for the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones that are in danger \Nof death! Can't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already too late to give \Nthat money to Captain Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they do that to the little \Nkid? Should we call sheriff in the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. This area is not \Ncovered by the country's law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he's a member of the Bluejam Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're paying money to the Nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be overlooked for any crime and \Nmurder they commit in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more dead body will draw \Nno one's attention here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit! Stop trying to \Nkeep a secret like a grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Sabo raid Porchemy's hideout to save the captured Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the overwhelming strength of the pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo finds a moment's opportunity to free Luffy and makes a run for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Ace shares a surprising resolution...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Won't Run! Ace's Desperate \NRescue Operation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
